Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: An Aqualish Sith was one of four of Darth Krayt's Order that ambushed four Jedi—including Ahn Rasi Tuum, Wolf Sazen, and Shado Vao—on the planet Daluuj in 137 ABY. He was cut in two at the torso by Master Sazen during the skirmish.
